scripts.plot-tmp: yarn run plot-tmp-c && yarn run plot-tmp-no-c
scripts.plot-tmp-c: psbr tex query combinations/combination_1/output combinations/combination_2/output combinations/combination_4/output combinations/combination_5/output -n 'plot_c' -q '^C' --svg --overrideCombinationLabels Comunica-HDT,Oxigraph-Rust,Oxigraph-JS-RDFJS,Jena
scripts.plot-tmp-no-c: psbr tex query combinations/combination_1/output combinations/combination_2/output combinations/combination_4/output combinations/combination_5/output -n 'plot_no_c' -q '^[^C]' --svg --overrideCombinationLabels Comunica-HDT,Oxigraph-Rust,Oxigraph-JS-RDFJS,Jena
